{"article_id":"L0HADbvxBDXl4b3o","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Since the onset of the pandemic , there has been a lot of confusion regarding face masks .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"At first , the U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention told the general public not to wear masks","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"if they aren ' t experiencing coronavirus symptoms","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"or caring for someone with coronavirus .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Then the agency reversed its guidance in early April","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"and advised Americans to wear non-N-95 masks or face cloth covering in places","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"where it is difficult to social distance .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Following the CDC ' s announcement ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"several states","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"including New York","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"adapted mandatory mask mandates .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"One study estimated","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that states","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that issued mandates between April and mid-May","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"averted as many as 230,000 coronavirus cases .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Others left it up to cities or counties to issue mandates .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"But amid a resurgence of coronavirus , states like California and Texas issued state mandates in late June and early July , respectively .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"A separate study estimates","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that nearly 45,000 U.S. deaths from coronavirus could be prevented by November","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"if 95 % of the population wore masks .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"The general consensus among infectious disease experts is that it will slow the spread","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"and prevent some transmission .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"But many have disregarded health-experts ' recommendations","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"based on scientific evidence","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and refuse to wear a mask","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"despite city- and state-wide mandates .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"See also :","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Why do so many Americans refuse to wear face masks ?","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Politics is part of it","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"- but only part","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Some see it as an infringement of personal freedom ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"while others may not wear masks","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"because of misconceptions","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"which have been shared widely on social media ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"said Peter Chin-Hong , an infectious disease physician at University of California San Francisco .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"1 . You don ' t need to wear a mask outside","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"since sunlight kills the virus","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"A study","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"published last month","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"estimated","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that \" 90 % or more of SARS-CoV-2 virus will be inactivated \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"after being exposed to midday sunlight for around 34 minutes .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"That ' s led some to believe","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that it is not necessary to wear a mask while outside .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"\" ' We have enough compelling data","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"to show","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that plenty of people get it outside","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"if they ' re close together","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"without a mask ' \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"- Peter Chin-Hong , an infectious disease physician at University of California San Francisco","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"But the catch is the study is only applicable to surfaces .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Meaning sunlight won ' t stop someone from spreading the virus","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"if they cough or sneeze near you","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"while you ' re outside ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Chin-Hong said .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"\" COVID likes people more than sunlight .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"It cares more about mouths and noses being near each other . \"","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"\" Overall this is a laboratory technical phenomenon","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that doesn ' t translate into human transmission .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"We have enough compelling data","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"to show","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that plenty of people get it outside","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"if they ' re close together","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"without a mask .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"2 . You only need to wear a mask","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"if you ' re experiencing symptoms","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"Asymptomatic and pre-symptomatic transmission accounts for more than half of the cases of coronavirus ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"according to a study","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"published in the Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences , a peer-reviewed journal on Monday .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"In the absence of common symptoms of coronavirus , a person","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"who has the virus","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"may not be prompted to get tested","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"and hence they don ' t self-isolate .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" ' We can say very clearly","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that wearing a mask is definitely helpful","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"in preventing acquisition as well as transmission. ' \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"- Anthony Fauci , director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"There is scant data on the percentage of cases of coronavirus","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that were prevented from wearing a mask ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Anthony Fauci , director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases told lawmakers during his June 23 Congressional testimony .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" We can say very clearly","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"that wearing a mask is definitely helpful","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"in preventing acquisition as well as transmission , \"","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" It is always better to have a mask on","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"than to not have a mask on , both for acquisition and for transmission , \"","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Fauci added .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"3 . Masks won ' t offer any protection for the person","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"wearing one","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"This is a more complicated one ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"rooted in truth .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"The rationale","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"for wearing a mask in the midst of the pandemic","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"is that it will act as a barrier","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"to prevent respiratory droplets from the mouth and nose from dispersing","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and transmitting the virus to others .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"That ' s considered to be the main way","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"the virus spreads .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"But isn ' t true 100 % that the mask-wearer themselves doesn ' t receive any protection from it ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Chin-Hong said .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"\" You will get some amount of protection from wearing a mask","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"because it ' s just like plexiglass .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"It will block droplets from hitting your nose or mouth . \"","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"4 . Wearing a mask will reduce your oxygen levels ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"right ?","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Wrong .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"On Facebook FB , -2.47 % , one widely shared post in May claimed","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"that wearing a mask will lower your oxygen levels .","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"( The post has since been taken down by Facebook .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"The company did not immediately respond multiple requests for a comment . )","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"\" In cases","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"where people have low oxygen levels","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"to begin with","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"that wearing a face mask won ' t lower their oxygen \"","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Another video","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"making the same claim","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"remains on Facebook","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"but has been flagged","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"for containing false information .","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"In the video , the user ,","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"who is a firefighter","depth":17},{"id":121,"text":"according to factcheck.org ,","depth":17},{"id":122,"text":"uses a multi-gas detector","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"to test the levels of oxygen in","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"he breaths in his mask .","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"After a couple of seconds of wearing a mask , he shows","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"that the oxygen in the air","depth":16},{"id":127,"text":"he ' s breathing","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"is lower .","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"( The user","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"who uploaded the video","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"did not immediately respond to a request for comment . )","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"Not only is the claim","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"he ' s making","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"wrong","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"but he also performed a flawed test","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"to arrive at that conclusion ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"Chin-Hong told .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"\" These are distractors , \"","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"\" It ' s dangerous to bring these thoughts to the public","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"when this public-health intervention can save lives . \"","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Even before coronavirus , face masks were given to patients","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"who have lung diseases","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"to protect others from them ,","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"And in cases","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"where people have low oxygen levels","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"to begin with","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"that wearing a face mask won ' t lower their oxygen levels .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"5 . Anything other than an N-95 mask is useless in terms of limiting transmission of the virus","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"\" The ' Tesla TSLA , -3.08 % of masks ' are N-95 masks , \"","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"Chin-Hong said ,","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"that ' s why they ' re reserved for frontline medical workers","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"who are caring for patients","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"who have contracted coronavirus .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"That said ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"a cloth mask , bandana or scarf is \" better","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"than not being protected at all. \"","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"Importantly , they provide a barrier to the respiratory droplets","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"that could come in contact with the wearer ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"Although several studies have attempted to uncover materials","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"that offer the greatest level of protection for a homemade mask ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"\" it ' s more important how comfortable you are","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"when you wear it . \"","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"\" They ' re like trying on a pair of jeans , \"","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"Even if your mask is made from a thin material ,","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"which studies have shown","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"offer less protection than a thicker material ,","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"if you ' re comfortable","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"while wearing it","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"you ' re less likely to touch your face","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"to make adjustments .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"Bottom line :","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"\" People are using all kinds of excuses","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"not to wear a mask","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"like saying","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"nothing works .","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"If you have high cholesterol","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"I ' m not saying","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"you won ' t get a heart attack","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"if you take medication ,","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"it ' s all about risk reduction , \"","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"Chin-Hong said .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":371,"left":0,"right":370,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":370,"left":219,"right":369,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":219,"left":204,"right":218,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":191,"right":203,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":191,"left":188,"right":190,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":1,"right":187,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":4,"right":189,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":194,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":7,"right":193,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":193,"left":192,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":197,"right":201,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":11,"right":196,"r